				In my oppinion the druid is, possibly, the best class in the game.  Druids are by nature(pun not intended) one of the most balanced classes; a wide variety of spells, friendship with animals, better fighters than clerics. etc.  However, when choosing the race of your druid I suggest halfling. Why? First you start off in the Misty Thicket, one of the best and most balanced newbie areas on Norrath. And second halfling druids are able to use scarab armor, with better ac than leather. <BR>
