			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I don't believe with all of the places mentioned to powerlevel a druid, Lavastorm was left out.<BR>
<BR>
You can go from 14 to lev 16 in virtually no time, and still get exp from the zone until lev 18.  The place is filled with summoned beings, which you can kite, and wap with expulse summoned in the interim.  If it's red, pull it, just stay out of it's way when you wrap around for another kiting pass...<BR>
<BR>
Check the zone map for more info.<BR>
<BR>
The only worry may be that good races will be KOSed in the connecting zone, but that's what cammo and sow are for.<BR>
<BR>
Mahdi, Druid of Tunare, Veeshan.
				</font>
